nl_querry: Which racetrack hosted the most recent race? Indicate the full location. full location refers to location+country; most recent race = MAX(date)
llm_querry: SELECT c.name AS racetrack_name, c.location, c.country FROM races AS r JOIN circuits AS c ON r.circuitId = c.circuitId WHERE r.date = (SELECT MAX(date) FROM races)
gold_querry: SELECT T1.location FROM circuits AS T1 INNER JOIN races AS T2 ON T1.circuitId = T2.circuitId ORDER BY T2.date DESC LIMIT 1
